Package: robgpu
Version: 0.0
Title: Robust Statistics on GPU
Author: First Last <first.last@mail.com>
Maintainer: First Last <first.last@mail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
SystemRequirements: Nvidia's CUDA toolkit (>= release 5.0)
Description: This package provides R interfaces to a handful of common
        functions implemented using the Nvidia CUDA toolkit. Some of
        the functions require at least GPU Compute Capability 1.3.
        Thanks to Craig Stark at UC Irvine for donating time on his
        lab's Mac.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/robgpu
NeedsCompilation: yes

